description: Gets member information for your organization.

parameters.name: accountId
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID of the member account to retrieve information on.

nested_items.name: accountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID of the member account.

nested_items.name: delegatedAdminAccountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID of the Amazon Inspector delegated administrator for this member account.

nested_items.name: relationshipStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the member account.

nested_items.name: updatedAt
nested_items.description: A timestamp showing when the status of this member was last updated.
